Things I’ve been doing that are bad for myself lately.😔
1. Grabbing my phone first thing in the morning & scrolling before I start my day.
2. Negative & critical self talk.
3. Snapping & not being a good partner. How can I be a good partner when I haven’t been good to myself?
4. Not allowing room for mistakes and being too hard on myself.

If you’ve been struggling lately know that it’s okay, we’re all just trying our best everyday. You deserve the kindness you give to others too.💗🦋🎀 #selfcaresunday #mentalhealthawareness #selflove #diorcapturetotale #tatchaskincare

10mins total ab workout that will set your abs on fire🔥 . Back in New York City and ready to get back into my routine! This workout is a killer, lmk what you think if you try it out! Created by my trainer @ahappykwan @thelivmethod 🏋🏻‍♀️🫶🏼🌼⛱️

Dead bug hold 30sec
Single leg toe taps x 5
Both legs x5
Straight leg toe taps x5
Both legs x 5
Shoulder taps x20
Plank spikes x5
Windshield wipers x20
Knee plank T-spine twist x20
Back extension holds 30s
Back extension torso twist x20

 #summerworkouts #abworkoutsfromhome #womenworkouts

Recipe below! Making apple pie cookies. Turned on my oven for the first time in my apartment to try out this simple recipe, so simple yet delicious, I ate 4 of them last night.🥧👩🏻‍🍳😮‍💨🍂🤎

Crust & lattice: 
1 pack of refrigerated pie crust 

Filling:
4 small apples
3 tbs brown sugar
3 tbs sugar
1 tbs flour
1/2 tsp cinnamon
1/2 tsp nutmeg 
1/2 lemon
1/4 cup water 

Shimmer for 15 mins

Create lattice + brush egg wash(1 egg + 1 tbs of water)
Bake at 350f for 30 mins.

Sprinkle cinnamon + sugar on top & serve! 🍎🥧

#applepiecookies #applepierecipe #fallactivities
